<% content_for :main do %>
  <div class="splash">
    <div class="splash-wrapper">
      <div class="splash-greeting">
        <h1 class="splash-header">Support journalism <br> with impact in Texas</h1>
        <p class="splash-info">Members and donors power our nonprofit newsroom. Please give what you can to support our essential work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="splash-donate">
        <%= partial "checkout" %>
        <p class="splash-once"><span class="weight--bold">Make a</span> <a class="splash-link--yellow" href="https://checkout.texastribune.org/donateform">one-time donation</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= partial 'campaign_desktop_nav' %>
  </div>

  <div class="main">
    <div class="main-left">
      <div class="section">
        <h3>This is how Texas Tribune journalism made a difference in 2017</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h4><a target="_blank" href="https://www.texastribune.org/2017/11/13/texas-capitol-victims-sexual-harassment-must-fend-themselves/">Sexual harassment</a></h4>
        <p>Our investigation into sexual malpractice at the Texas Capitol led lawmakers to dismantle their existing sexual harassment rules and put sweeping new policies in place.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h4><a target="_blank" href="https://www.texastribune.org/organizations/texas-alcoholic-beverage-commission/">Texas Alcoholic Beverage Commission investigation</a></h4>
        <p>Top TABC officials were ousted amid our investigation into junkets and bad behavior at the taxpayer-funded agency.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="small-img clearfix">
        <figure class="small-img__fig">
          <img class="small-img__file" src="./img/harvey-reporters.jpg">
          <figcaption class="small-img__caption">As rescue boats and trucks navigated a West Houston neighborhood flooded by Hurricane Harvey, Neena Satija (left) and Kiah Collier (right) documented the recovery efforts.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </aside>

      <div class="section">
        <h4><a target="_blank" href="https://www.texastribune.org/series/in-harveys-wake/">Hurricane Harvey</a></h4>
        <p>We predicted the flooding in 2016, meaning when the storm actually hit, our readers had a reference for why it had happened â€” and a slate of experts to follow during and after.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h4><a target="_blank" href="https://www.texastribune.org/2017/10/27/texas-missing-payments-rental-furniture-can-land-you-jail/">Rent-to-own investigation</a></h4>
        <p>Lawmakers on both sides of the aisle immediately pledged reforms after we revealed people being jailed and criminally prosecuted for missing a payment on a couch.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h4><a target="_blank" href="https://apps.texastribune.org/sold-out/">Sold Out</a></h4>
        <p>Following our series on child sex trafficking in Texas, which was jointly viewed by hundreds of thousands of readers in Cosmopolitan Magazine, the state hired its first-ever director of human trafficking prevention.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-right">
